01:05:47.443 --> 01:05:49.212
Bibigyan din kita ng pagkakataon.

1141
01:05:49.236 --> 01:05:51.772
Makakakuha ka ng tatlong segundo...

1142
01:05:51.822 --> 01:05:53.508
para mawala!

1143
01:05:53.532 --> 01:05:55.317
Isa.

1144
01:05:55.743 --> 01:05:57.361
Dalawa.

1145
01:05:57.954 --> 01:06:00.474
Teka, darn it.

1146
01:06:00.498 --> 01:06:03.492
Tatlo! Hinahamon kita sa isang tunggalian!

1147
01:06:07.046 --> 01:06:08.872
Saan siya...?

1148
01:06:09.340 --> 01:06:11.291
Nahulog ba siya?

1149
01:06:16.222 --> 01:06:18.158
Hi, Kang-ho.

1150
01:06:18.182 --> 01:06:20.342
May hinahanap ka ba?

1151
01:07:21.954 --> 01:07:23.864
Kang-ho!

1152
01:07:51.609 --> 01:07:52.586
Kang-ho!

1153
01:07:52.610 --> 01:07:54.603
Kang-ho!

1154
01:08:23.808 --> 01:08:27.853
<i><font color="#ffff00">Gustong-gusto kita.</font></i>

1155
01:08:57.007 --> 01:08:58.917
<i>Choi Kang-ho!</i>

1156
01:09:23.325 --> 01:09:25.360
patay na ako.

1157
01:09:35.838 --> 01:09:37.581
Natagpuan ito.

1158
01:09:38.883 --> 01:09:41.376
nahanap ko na!

1159
01:09:43.179 --> 01:09:46.074
Ye-jin, Seo-jin! nahanap ko na!

1160
01:09:46.098 --> 01:09:47.841
nahanap ko na!

1161
01:09:58.444 --> 01:10:01.021
Isa, dalawa, tatlo.

1162
01:10:01.739 --> 01:10:03.481
nahanap ko na.

1163
01:10:04.366 --> 01:10:07.777
kaya ko to. Kaya kong ibaba ito.

1164
01:10:17.630 --> 01:10:20.790
Ye-jin! Seo-jin!

1165
01:10:29.892 --> 01:10:32.093
Ye-jin! Seo-jin!

1166
01:10:33.437 --> 01:10:36.431
Ye-jin! Seo-jin!

1167
01:10:40.778 --> 01:10:42.854
Sino ito?

1168
01:11:07.388 --> 01:11:10.307
<i><font color="#ffff00">Ang Mabuting Masamang Ina</font></i>

1169
01:11:25.447 --> 01:11:27.732
<i>Isang taong hindi ko kilala.</i>

1170
01:11:27.783 --> 01:11:29.594
<i>Pero masakit dito.</i>

1171
01:11:29.618 --> 01:11:31.179
<i>At ito ay isang bagay...</i>

1172
01:11:31.203 --> 01:11:33.571
<i>kailangan mong gawin nang mag-isa.</i>

1173
01:11:34.331 --> 01:11:37.185
<i>Kung sakaling makasagabal ka sa akin,</i>

1174
01:11:37.209 --> 01:11:38.645
<i>Hindi ko ito pahihintulutan.</i>

1175
01:11:38.669 --> 01:11:41.648
{\an8}<i>Nabulok ako sa bilangguan ng ilang buwan dahil sa iyo!</i>

1176
01:11:41.672 --> 01:11:44.985
{\an8}<i>Paglabag sa Artikulo 49, Talata 1,
Aytem 10 ng Road Traffic Act.</i>

1177
01:11:45.009 --> 01:11:47.794
{\an8}<i>- Hindi ko siya kailanman kaibigan.
- Mi-joo?</i>

1178
01:11:48.887 --> 01:11:50.073
{\an8}<i>Mi-joo.</i>

1179
01:11:50.097 --> 01:11:51.241
{\an8}<i>Naaalala mo ba siya?</i>

1180
01:11:51.265 --> 01:11:53.910
{\an8}<i>Mula nang bumalik ka dala ang lahat ng gamit mo,</i>

1181
01:11:53.934 --> 01:11:56.454
{\an8}<i>tila naparito ka upang manatili.</i>

1182
01:11:56.478 --> 01:11:59.749
{\an8}<i>Alam kong hindi naging madali para sa iyo
darating. Magkasama tayo.</i>

1183
01:11:59.773 --> 01:12:00.709
{\an8}<i>Huwag mo siyang tawagan.</i>

1184
01:12:00.733 --> 01:12:04.394
{\an8}<i>Huwag na siyang makilala o makipaglaro muli.</i>

